### Test Analytics Anomalies Endpoint
### GET /gov/analytics/anomalies
### Detects unusual spikes in report volumes

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get anomalies (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/anomalies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "3201-1-1234567890",
#       "regionName": "Kota Bandung",
#       "categoryName": "Jalan Rusak",
#       "spikePercent": 250.5,
#       "hoursAgo": 24,
#       "reportCount": 15
#     }
#   ]
# }
